beer.beer_description:
Wheat Hefeweizen style beer, the traditional" Švyturys "collection member. It has a refreshing taste and aroma that is reminiscent of cloves, banana, plum, orange peel and exotic fruit bouquet. Unfiltered, cloudy, distinctive, exceptional flavor beer seasoned recommended a slice of lemon and a special drink chilled cup. 
 
Kvietiniam designed beer glass - a significant praplatėjanti the top of his form somewhat reminiscent of an hourglass, so perfectly reveals the distinctive flavor of the beer. "Švyturys" white "beer perfectly with fish, seafood, soft cheeses and light fruit desserts.
